{"tid":2175423,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本] [多圖] 小丸子 多汁 觸手","createTime":"2020-08-26T12:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T17:01:55.000Z","uid":113525,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74809d1bcd171547cf7d66f0b8939d26b84637a5","tid":2175423,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:43:30.000Z","msg":"小丸子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UktmcCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUktmcCP.jpg&h=2bc96616&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n多汁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXWu5X6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXWu5X6.jpg&h=1f1ad6c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n觸手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6M3qYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6M3qYA.jpg&h=94412897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日想食章魚燒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n製成品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5TmcDY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5TmcDY.jpg&h=8b9c7857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n切左椰菜同埋蔥先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEhYZi7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEhYZi7.jpg&h=0131f569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8DtB5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8DtB5Q.jpg&h=e1fcba62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八爪魚刺身切粒，用普通八爪魚都得，但就要落d鹽煮一煮佢先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g75r8cz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg75r8cz.jpg&h=cf3a2295&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n將蛋，麵粉，牛奶同埋木魚湯撈勻，再加鹽同黑胡椒調味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmSBL0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmSBL0c.jpg&h=6a357c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加熱章魚燒板，落油，倒入麵糊，7分滿就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbFS3Ni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbFS3Ni.jpg&h=83953e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加埋八爪魚，天婦羅麵衣，椰菜絲同埋蔥粒，之後再倒麵糊，要蓋過哂d材料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkH9506.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkH9506.jpg&h=7dc36c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煎到咁上下就用枝野轉粒章魚燒，突出黎既部份收係底就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1p6KUUO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1p6KUUO.jpg&h=40abf9a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等到金黃色就得，唧埋章魚燒醬同埋沙律醬上去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Mg68e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Mg68e9.jpg&h=0a43e1d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加埋紫菜絲同鰹魚片，食得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sEwfg8N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsEwfg8N.png&h=6cf991fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食評: 八爪魚刺身好鮮甜，加左牛奶同木魚湯落麵糊度，個層次感多左，好鬼好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣既可以睇下條片同埋記得訂閱我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ocu6BcAfhZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Focu6BcAfhZw&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=278c2933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ocu6BcAfhZw</a><br />\n<br />\nIG :<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/eatingaroundthe_World/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Featingaroundthe_World%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=b7b9754f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/eatingaroundthe_World/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日九龍灣呢單野完全示範緊咩叫抗爭典範<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2170925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2170925</a>"},{"pid":"0cd580a3da90d3c6b96f32b786ac96b56976bbb3","tid":2175423,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:43:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec258b3f355d4b19d46615dc707e802a9d170eee","tid":2175423,"uid":289458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"訂閱左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e68ad2bbe025c3cba7ebefa53aae7442b1e1236","tid":2175423,"uid":113525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec258b3f355d4b19d46615dc707e802a9d170eee","tid":2175423,"uid":289458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"訂閱左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ef90e