e326daec8d88535","tid":2175423,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddb0904a8c58fd0b001489f14372ae1dc9b0cbd6","tid":2175423,"uid":166733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"Bruno d機點睇 見好似都有小丸子板"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"冇用過 但聽講邊位火力會弱D <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都用得過既應該 我見有好多隻顏色 好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}